    <div class="bs-docs-section clearfix">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="well">
                <div class="col-lg-1">
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-5">
                    <h3>
                        FlowTasks is an open source project that helps you improve the way your organization works.
                        <br />
                        <br />

                        Imagine all your business processes synchronized and managed by an automated system.
                        <br />
                        <br />

                        Imagine all your team communication easily accessible everywhere.
