    <div class="bs-docs-section clearfix">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-4 ">
                <h2 class="title">Framework for process automation</h2>
                <p>
                    With FlowTasks you can automate all the processes in your organization.
                    In the backend it uses Microsoft workflow engine. It hides all the plumbing
                    so that you can focus only on the important things that matter to you...
                    Improving your organization!
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <h2 class="title">Easily customizable for every environment</h2>
                <p>
                    FlowTasks provides you with a wide range of functionalities to easily connect
                    workflows to your system and design tasks based on the needs of your organization.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <h2 class="title">Every one can design workflows</h2>
                <p>
                    FlowTasks has an easy an intuitive workflow designer that all levels of the
                    business can use to design the process workflow. The developers can then complete
                    the development and deploy the workflow. This eliminates the comunication gap
                    that sometimes exists between developers and other parts of the business.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-4 ">
                <h2 class="title">Stay in touch</h2>
                <p>
                    With FlowTasks you can send messages to all members or groups in your organization.
                    You'll always be connected with all the people you need to get your job done.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <h2 class="title">Keep track of all the work done</h2>
                <p>
                    FlowTasks stores important information about all the workflows in your system.
                    So you'll always know what's happend or is happening in your organization.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <h2 class="title">Monitor your organization</h2>
                <p>
                    Flowtasks collects a lot of data that can then be reviewed through a series of
                    reports. You can gather useful information like the workload of your employees or the
                    performance of your business processes.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
